OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FA woman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,7,Fhas been arrested during a six-month
OL,8,Ftrial of live facial recognition in
OL,9,Fsouth London.
OL,11,FIn total 173 suspects were arrested
OL,12,Ffor crimes including kidnap, rape and
OL,13,Fserious sexual assault during the
OL,14,Fpilot in Croydon, during which static
OL,15,Fcameras rather than vans were used for
OL,16,Fthe first time.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
