OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said that
OL,7,Fcrime in the area reduced by 10.5%
OL,8,Fduring the trial, which took place
OL,9,Fbetween October 2025 and March 2026,
OL,10,Fincluding a 21% reduction in violence
OL,11,Fagainst women and girls.
OL,13,FThe static cameras, placed on Croydon
OL,14,FHigh Street, were used in 24
OL,15,Foperations, with arrests including a
OL,16,F36-year-old woman who was wanted for
OL,17,Ffailing to appear at court for an
OL,18,Fassault in 2004.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
