CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, 7 October 2025, Nilton
OL,7,FDarame, 25, of Loughborough Street,
OL,8,FLambeth was alerted by the static
OL,9,Fcameras in Croydon.
OL,11,FDarame was found to be in breach of
OL,12,Ftag conditions, in relation to an
OL,13,Fintentional strangulation and two
OL,14,Fcounts of assault on an emergency
OL,15,Fworker on Monday, 8 September 2025 and
OL,16,Farrested.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced at Croydon Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Thursday, 8 January to 18
OL,20,Fmonths' imprisonment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
