PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FA month later, at a static deployment
OL,7,Fon Friday, 21 November 2025, Kastriot
OL,8,FKrrashi, 35, of Dingwall Road,
OL,9,FCroydon, was stopped by officers for
OL,10,Fbeing wanted on suspicion of breaching
OL,11,Fhis conditions as a registered sex
OL,12,Foffender.
OL,14,FHe was arrested, and sentenced at Wood
OL,15,FGreen Crown Court on Friday, 13
OL,16,FFebruary to six months' imprisonment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
