CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FOn Friday, 16 January, Neville Cohen,
OL,7,F55, of no fixed address, was stopped
OL,8,Fby officers for being wanted for
OL,9,Ffailing to comply with a condition on
OL,10,Fa Sexual Harm Prevention Order (SHPO)
OL,11,Fwhich required him to attend Croydon
OL,12,FPolice Station in October 2025.
OL,14,FHe attempted to flee from officers and
OL,15,Fwas arrested and later sentenced to
OL,16,Ffour months' imprisonment on Saturday,
OL,17,F17 January at Croydon Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
