PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FA 31-year-old man who was wanted for
OL,7,Fvoyeurism for more than six months was
OL,8,Falso arrested, as well as a 41-year-
OL,9,Fold man who was wanted in connection
OL,10,Fwith a rape in November in Croydon.
OL,12,FLindsey Chiswick, live facial
OL,13,Frecognition lead for the Metropolitan
OL,14,FPolice, said: "These results show why
OL,15,Flive facial recognition is such a
OL,16,Fpowerful tool when it's used
OL,17,Fcarefully, openly and in the right
OL,18,Fplaces.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778847105
OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,F"Crime in this area is down by more
OL,7,Fthan 10%, and the public can see the
OL,8,Fdifference.
OL,10,F"This technology is helping us find
OL,11,Fpeople wanted by the courts, identify
OL,12,Fserious offenders quickly and focus
OL,13,Four resources where they make the
OL,14,Fbiggest impact, all with exceptional
OL,15,Faccuracy.
OL,17,F"We will continue using static cameras
OL,18,Fin Croydon as part of our regular live
OL,19,Ffacial recognition deployments which
OL,20,Fplay a vital part in keeping London
OL,21,Fsafe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU}D@FO]
