OL,3,CPerson arrested every 35 minutes in
OL,4,Clive facial recognition pilot
OL,6,FMore than 470,000 people walked past
OL,7,Fthe camera during the pilot, which saw
OL,8,Fone false alert for which the person
OL,9,Fwas spoken to by officers and then
OL,10,Fallowed to leave.
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,13,Four political experts are across all
OL,14,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,15,Fto the latest episode below...
